{"tid":1046121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】美女站視線死角遭鏟起　連同廢土倒進碎石機","createTime":"2019-03-04T04:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T05:26:10.000Z","uid":61543,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ff966bfe0183f25d43395e8729b088297cdf8282","tid":1046121,"uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T04:10:08.000Z","msg":"《微博》近日瘋傳一段影片，中國一名女子在陶瓷工廠任職，於上月24日上午9時許佇立在廠內作業區，緊盯著施工環節並看著一輛藍色大貨車倒車，沒想到後方的堆土機司機因視線死角，連同廢土一併將她鏟起，並一同倒入砂土粉碎機中。<br />\n過程中其他工人疑似聽見女子的慘叫聲，司機趕緊下車並呼叫其他同事，一同前往砂土粉碎機內查看女子狀況，最後結果不得而知。最後這段影片被轉發至《臉書》公開社團「聯結車 大貨車 大客車 拉拉隊 運輸業 照片影片資訊分享團」，許多專業的人士表示「應該是攪進去了」、「那是震動碎石機！把殘雜有土石的沙石丟進去變成細沙土！」、「沒意外應該是砂土粉碎機，把砂土跟石頭攪碎成一樣大小」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190304/1526698\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190304%2F1526698&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4AjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=a6f3caea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190304%2F1526698&h=95bb0b76\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190304/1526698</a>"},{"pid":"17de16d7610fcca29201a885db35651e430788e9","tid":1046121,"uid":78304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T04:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />整唔到治癒gif"},{"pid":"c4c299265f740b30794229e5f64283834b099425","tid":1046121,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T04:14:11.000Z","msg":"睇未都痛"},{"pid":"faa436756679bb04fa47ab598cbd84d833dd2ad2","tid":1046121,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T04:14:19.000Z","msg":"腦魔又有素材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0437b11d0a672cca09e2e5dc1cdaec58841ffb74","tid":1046121,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4c299265f740b30794229e5f64283834b0